ton\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hfb1665702796355.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hfb1665702796355.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hfb1665702796355.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hfb1665702796355\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      IncludeScript Library Editor\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use the IncludeScript Library Editor to create and edit IncludeScript objects, and edit the properties of the library itself.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hfb1665702796355__section_w14ab1b7b1_w15ab1b7_w16ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hfb1665702796355__section_w17ab1b7b3_w18ab1b7_w19ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d231698e60\">\n                       \n Worksheets\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hfb1665702796355__li_d2696e1_d2697e1_d2698e1\">Define Structure—create new IncludeScript objects and edit their properties.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hfb1665702796355__li_d2699e1_d2700e1_d2701e1\">Write Script—write the code for the IncludeScript.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hfb1665702796355__section_w20ab1b7b5_w21ab1b7_w22ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d231698e75\">\n                       \n How to\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hfb1665702796355__li_d2702e1_d2703e1_d2704e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xiu1704441843991.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xiu1704441843991.html\" title=\"An IncludeScript may define a fragment of code or a complete ProcScript module. It is only compiled when the object that uses it is compiled. To create an IncludeScript, add it to an IncludeScript Library.\">Create an IncludeScript</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hfb1665702796355__li_d2705e1_d2706e1_d2707e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qle1665702773192.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qle1665702773192.html\" title=\"Use the Uniface IDE to develop an application, following the Uniface development paradigm of Model, Construct, Build, and Deploy.\">Using the Uniface IDE</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hfb1665702796355__li_d2708e1_d2709e1_d2710e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dkp1665702773261.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dkp1665702773261.html\" title=\"Although development objects can be quite different in content and purpose, the way you create, edit and delete them in the Uniface IDE is essentially the same.\">Working with Development Objects</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hdr1665702713345.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>IncludeScript Library</a><p>An IncludeScript Library contains IncludeScript objects, which can be inserted into ProcScript using the #include directive and are resolved during compilation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fbw1665702713269.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>IncludeScript</a><p>An IncludeScript is a Development Object that defines a fragment of script that can be inserted into ProcScript using the #include directive.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kee1692183917031.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Libraries</a><p>Libraries are collections of objects that can be shared in some way, either during development, or at runtime. They are main development objects, so whenever they are saved or exported, all the objects that they contain are included.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528187\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528187\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "IncludeScript Library Editor Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 IncludeScript Library Editor Use the IncludeScript Library Editor to create and edit IncludeScript objects, and edit the properties of the library itself. Worksheets Define Structure—create new IncludeScript objects and edit their properties. Write Script—write the code for the IncludeScript. How to Create an IncludeScript Using the Uniface IDE Working with Development Objects Related Links IncludeScript Library An IncludeScript Library contains IncludeScript objects, which can be inserted into ProcScript using the #include directive and are resolved during compilation. IncludeScript An IncludeScript is a Development Object that defines a fragment of script that can be inserted into ProcScript using the #include directive. Libraries Libraries are collections of objects that can be shared in some way, either during development, or at runtime. They are main development objects, so whenever they are saved or exported, all the objects that they contain are included. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}